        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Separate 2<strong> leaves</strong> per person from the<strong> lettuce</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>inner core[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into quarters lengthways</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-3-1684248637508-x200.jpg",
