            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are almost ready, drain your <strong>pineapple</strong> <strong>slices</strong> and add them to a separate baking tray, then push into 2 piles per person</p><p>Top the <strong>pineapple slices</strong> with the <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> to the tray and put in the oven for 5 min or until they're hot and crusty and the cheese is melted</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
