    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Once pulled, mix the <strong>chicken</strong> in with the pan juices – this is your <strong>shredded fiery chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
