            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> ciabattas</strong> in half</p><p>Assemble each <strong>ciabatta</strong> with a <strong>lettuce leaf</strong>,<strong> </strong>a<strong> cheesy pineapple slice</strong>,<strong> </strong>the<strong> shredded fiery chicken</strong>, another<strong> lettuce leaf</strong>,<strong> cheesy pineapple slice</strong> and finally a dollop of <strong>pineapple mayo</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>lettuce</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> on the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
